Content: A high-level Myanmar Navy delegation, headed by Navy Commander of Myanmar during a tour to the upcountry paid their homage to the Temple of Tooth (Sri Dalada Maligawa) on 23 October. Major General T.J Nanayakkara, General Officer Commanding, 11 Division welcomed the visiting foreign  delegation by offering trays of flowers and accompanied them to the inner chamber for veneration. The delegation visited the museum and the surroundings before they left the place.
